## Set Wallpaper in Hyprland

# WALLPAPER='/home/kay/.config/hypr/wallpapers/wallpaper.jpg'
# WALLPAPER='/home/kay/.config/hypr/wallpapers/wallpaper-alt.jpg'
WALLPAPER='/home/kay/.config/hypr/wallpapers/ad66173fbfb98ff0458cfc7cd1d4be12.jpg'

swaybg --output '*' --mode fill --image "$WALLPAPER"
